summary: This mod is a conversion of Sexy Transparent Zipsuit - 7BASE UNPB CBBE BODYSLIDE with optional TBBP support by nakrulz to the CHSBHC body.
descriptionHtml:
-----------------[IMG]http://i58.tinypic.com/2m4odg5.jpg[/IMG]-----------------
This mod is a conversion of Sexy Transparent Zipsuit - 7BASE UNPB CBBE BODYSLIDE with optional TBBP support by nakrulz to the CHSBHC body.It is a light armor and has an armor value equal to dragonscale gears.The armor can be crafted at the forging station under LEATHER section. Or if you decide to cheat then open console with ~ then type: help "zipsuit" then use player.additem [item number] [amount]

------------------------ [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/2hpskkp.jpg[/IMG]------------------------

Thanks to Bethesda for an amazing game
Thanks to The Nexus for hosting this mod
